input: (relevent feilds are only sent)
------

{
    "applicationId":"67fcd5ac6d8d02d21351fcff",
    "data":{
        "status":"published"
    }
}

output:
------

200
{message:"status updated"}
{message:"data updated"}

404
{message:"application not provided"}
{message:"no data provided"}

409
{message:"application not found"}
{message:"application already published"}
{message:"wrong data given"}
{message:`application can be converted to ${status}`}

500
{
    message:"internal server error",
    error:error.message
}